info.name: Royal Paneer Curry Combo (Serves 1)
info.description: (Choice Paneer Curries with Breads) Enjoy a dumdaar paneer daawat with an indulgent paneer curry and bread of your choice. Also, don't forget to add a refreshing beverage!

info.name: Aftaabi Paneer Tikka Masala
info.description: Savour tender, char-grilled paneer chunks with this authentic tikka masala curry. A mouthwatering combination of flavour and texture, indulge in this lajawab paneer peshkash for a royal daawat!

info.name: Nafees Laccha Paratha (Pack of 2)
info.description: Make it an indulgent daawat with these flaky parathas, fried until crispy with desi ghee. Nothing beats these crowd favourite flatbreads for a wholesome meal.

info.name: Nafees Laccha Paratha (Pack of 4)
info.description: Make it an indulgent daawat with these flaky parathas, fried until crispy with desi ghee. Nothing beats these crowd favourite flatbreads for a wholesome meal.

info.name: Durbari Tawa Paratha (Pack of 3)
info.description: Have an indulgent and satisfying feast with these large, triangular shaped parathas seared on tawa until crispy. Nothing beats these crispy parathas for a wholesome meal.

info.name: Shaandaar Paneer Curries Combo (Serves 2)
info.description:
1 Paneer Curry (500gm), Choice of Bread (Pack of 4), Kebab (6pcs) and a Beverage.
Daawat ka aaghaz karein with your favourite paneer curry and bread and pair it with a lajawab kebab and beverage.

info.name: Rivayati Paneer Curry Combo (Serves 2)
info.description:
Paneer Curry (500 gm) with Choice of Bread (Pack of 4).
Set up a wholesome daawat for 2 with your choice of North Indian paneer curry and breads.

info.name: Falafel-E-Khaas
info.description: Savour the great taste with shallow fried chickpea nuggets with a blend of aromatic spices.

info.name: Beetroot & Peanut Kebab
info.description: Savour the flavours of handpicked fresh beetroots and roasted peanuts with a subtle hint of spices. These royal beetroot kebabs are crisp on the outside and soft on the inside.

info.name: Dahi Labneh Kebab
info.description: Crafted by Celebrity Chef Kunal Kapur and enriched with gentle flavours of Curd, this kebab is delicately spiced with cumin and ginger & beautifully complements the royal biryani

info.name: Hara Bhara Kebab
info.description: Savour the goodness of finely minced potatoes, garden-fresh spinach and green peas, gently spiced with shahi masalas and shallow-fried to perfection. Coated with a generous layer of bread crumbs, these tender yet crispy kebabs will brighten up your daawat.

info.name: Aloo Chaap Tikki
info.description: A street favourite recipe that now resides in our royal kitchens. A mix of mashed potatoes, fresh coriander, chilies and onions, shallow-fried to form the perfect tea-time snack.

info.name: Beetroot & Peanut Kebab (6 pcs) & Hara Bhara Kebab (6 Pcs) Combo
info.description: Delicately spiced kebabs made with fresh beetroots & peanuts are served alongside the tender yet crispy Hara Bhara kebabs that are crafted with finely minced vegetables and shallow-fried to perfection.

info.name: Dahi Labneh Kebab (6 pcs) & Beetroot and Peanut Kebab (6 pcs) Combo
info.description: Subtly spiced with cumin and ginger, our Dahi Labneh Kebabs are served as a combo alongside kebabs made with handpicked fresh beetroots & crushed peanuts.

info.name: Dahi Labneh Kebab (6 pcs) & Hara Bhara Kebab (6 Pcs) Combo
info.description: Delicately spiced with cumin and ginger, our Dahi Labneh Kebabs are served as a combo alongside Hara Bhara kebabs that are crafted with finely minced vegetables and shallow-fried to perfection.

info.name: Zaikedaar Paneer Biryani (Paneer Dum Biryani - Serves 1)
info.description: (Served with 1 Gulab Jamun & Mint Raita) In this extravagant dish, soft & crumbly, fresh paneer is marinated with exquisite royal spices & layered with basmati to create a dish that is as delectable as it is extravagant.

info.name: Subz-e-Biryani (Dum Veg Biryani - Serves 1)
info.description: (Served with 1 Gulab Jamun & Mint Raita) Adorned with fresh vegetables, golden-hued long-grain basmati, & the coveted Behrouz spice mix, this dish will lend you an experience unlike any other.

info.name: Paneer Subz Biryani (Paneer Dum and Veg Biryani - Serves 1)
info.description: (Served with 1 Gulab Jamun & Mint Raita) In this immaculately balanced culinary masterpiece, diced fresh vegetables infused with succulent pieces of spiced paneer are layered on a bed of aromatic rice.

info.name: Taj-e-Khumb Biryani (Mushroom Biryani - Serves 1)
info.description: (Served with 1 Gulab Jamun & Mint Raita) Prepared with large chunks of tender, marinated mushrooms, this unique peshkash is adorned with the flavour of 23 shahi masalas and golden-hued basmati. Indulge in a ruhaani daawat with this flavourful veg biryani, as grand as the Taj!

info.name: Mughlai Gravy
info.description: Mughlai Gravy, a classic popular North India dish has a thick & creamy gravy with a flavor of yogurt and the taste of ground and whole spices.

info.name: Mirchi Ka Salan
info.description: Indulge your taste buds in this masaledaar peshkash, made with fine groundnuts, sesame seeds, tamarind, coconut & a blend of royal aromatic spices. Pair this spicy, tangy salan made of curried green chillies with your favourite biryani.

info.name: Royal Baklava (3 Pcs)
info.description: Introducing the Royal Baklava, an artisanal pastry all the way from the treasured corners of the Middle East. Baked to perfection, our specially curated box of rich, flaky baklava is filled with nutty exquisite pistachios, almonds and cashews, making it a charming nazraana for every celebration.

info.name: Chocolate Mousse
info.description: A delightful dose of rich chocolate with a velvety texture, perfect for satisfying your sudden chocolate cravings.

info.name: Gajar Halwa (100 gm)
info.description: Indulge in the comforting warmth of our aromatic Gajar Halwa, a classic Indian dessert crafted with freshly grated carrots, simmered in milk, ghee, and garnished with almonds, Perfect for one with Indian sweet cravings

info.name: Moong Dal Halwa (100 gm)
info.description: Add this rich & decadent Indian dessert made with moong lentils, ghee, milk, sugar, garnished with chopped dry-fruits. Perfect for one with Indian sweet cravings

info.name: Mint Raita
info.description: Mint raita is a refreshing and cooling raita made with mint, whisk yogurt and cumin.
